name: Randomkittens
body:
### Welcome to Random kittens. When it hasn't been your day, your week, your month, or even your year, but

Kittens'll be there for you
(When the rain starts to pour)
Kittens'll be there for you
(Like they've been there before)
Kittens'll be there for you
('Cause you're there for them too)
Freely inspired by [Friends OST](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=813bZYxnwYA)
Thanks also to [http://placekitten.com/](http://placekitten.com/) ### Authors and Contributors Me.
http://placekitten.com/
